- Check if you have run all tests according to mise.toml `mise docker-test` should do everything
- If there are errors, fix them and repeat the test execution and fixing until everything is resolved automaticaly
- When it's okay, update the project documentation in md files, write completed items to CHNAGELOG.md and remove them from TODO.md
- If the change is useful for the user and should know about it, write it also into README.md
- Commit all files `git add .; git commit -m "characteristic of changes within 100 characters

description of changes"`
- describe in chat of what you did for the user
